"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532080\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532080\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sns1665703134551.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sns1665703134551.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sns1665703134551.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sns1665703134551\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"sns1665703134551__ugputc_404693\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Copy data into an occurrence of the specified entity, which has been initialized by\n         <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugput</code>. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"sns1665703134551__topic_d121247e1_d121248e1_d121249e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sns1665703134551_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sns1665703134551__codeblock_erv_v1b_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">short ugput (unsigned char*entity, unsigned char*buffer, shortlen):</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sns1665703134551__topic_d86077e1_d86078e1_d86079e1_d86080e1_d86081e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d264774e64\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"sns1665703134551__parml_gfs_w1b_1wb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">The name of the entity you want to work on. A value of NULL or an empty string\n                  denotes the current entity. The entity must be painted on the component, and it\n                  must be defined in the application model.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">buffer</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">The data to be used. This data must be in DBMS storage format.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">len</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">The number of bytes to be copied from the buffer to the occurrence. Specify a\n                  negative value to indicate that more data is to follow. The absolute value of this\n                  number should not exceed the size of the buffer.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sns1665703134551__topic_d86082e1_d86083e1_d86084e1_d86085e1_d86086e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d264774e103\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sns1665703134551__table_d14891e1_d14892e1_d14893e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by ugputc</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sns1665703134551__table_d14891e1_d14892e1_d14893e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sns1665703134551__table_d14891e1_d14892e1_d14893e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sns1665703134551__table_d14891e1_d14892e1_d14893e1__entry__1\">&gt;1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sns1665703134551__table_d14891e1_d14892e1_d14893e1__entry__2\">The total number of bytes copied by this call\n                        and by previous calls to <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugputc</code> (returned when\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">Len</var> &gt; 1)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sns1665703134551__table_d14891e1_d14892e1_d14893e1__entry__1\">1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sns1665703134551__table_d14891e1_d14892e1_d14893e1__entry__2\">Uniface expects more data to be copied\n                        (returned when <var class=\"keyword varname\">Len</var> &lt; 0)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sns1665703134551__table_d14891e1_d14892e1_d14893e1__entry__1\">&lt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sns1665703134551__table_d14891e1_d14892e1_d14893e1__entry__2\">The occurrence was not initialized with a call\n                        to <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugput</code>, or the entity is not a painted database\n                        entity</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sns1665703134551__topic_d86087e1_d86088e1_d86089e1_d86090e1_d86091e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d264774e176\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sns1665703134551__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sns1665703134551__topic_d86092e1_d86093e1_d86094e1_d86095e1_d86096e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d264774e189\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sns1665703134551__p_d121277e1_d121278e1_d121279e1\">Use <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugputc</code> to move data from\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">buffer</var> to an occurrence of <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> that was\n            initialized with <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugput</code>. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> is NULL or an\n            empty string, the current entity is used. The data in <var class=\"keyword varname\">buffer</var> should\n            be in DBMS storage format.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sns1665703134551__p_d121280e1_d121281e1_d121282e1\">Do not supply primary key values that are different\n            from the values that were passed to <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugput</code>. Uniface does not check on\n            this, and will use the values passed to <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugputc</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sns1665703134551__p_d121283e1_d121284e1_d121285e1\">Use a negative value for <var class=\"keyword varname\">len</var> to\n            indicate that there is more data to be moved to the occurrence. Use a non-negative value\n            to indicate that the current block is the last block of data. This makes it possible to\n            fill a large occurrence using a small buffer by repeated calls to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugputc</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sns1665703134551__p_d121286e1_d121287e1_d121288e1\">The processing is not complete until you call\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugputc</code> one last time with a non-negative value for\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">len</var>. Once this is done, further calls to <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugputc</code>\n            will return -1 until <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugput</code> is called again to initialize a new\n            occurrence.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sns1665703134551__section_qlr_cbb_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d264774e250\">Example: Calling ugputc Repeatedly</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following simple example illustrates how to fill an occurrence of the\n            current entity with the value ‘<code class=\"ph codeph\">abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz</code>’ by repeated\n            calls to <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugputc</code> with a length of -1. Note the concluding call to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugputc</code> with a zero length; without that call, the data will not be\n            shown in the component.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sns1665703134551_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sns1665703134551__codeblock_jkg_2bb_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\nEXPORT void fill_occ ()\n{\nint i;\n\nugput(0, 0, 0); /* Initialize the occurrence */\n\nfor ( i=0; i&lt;26; i++ )\n{\nchar ch = 'a'+i;\ngputc(0, &amp;ch, -1); /* Add one alphabet character */\n}\n\nugputc(0, 0, 0); /* Terminate processing */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxb1665703134482.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ugput</a><p>Initialize an occurrence of the specified entity for subsequent calls to ugputc.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532080\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532080\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ugputc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Copy data into an occurrence of the specified entity, which has been initialized by ugput . Explain this code short ugput (unsigned char*entity, unsigned char*buffer, shortlen): Copy Parameters entity The name of the entity you want to work on. A value of NULL or an empty string denotes the current entity. The entity must be painted on the component, and it must be defined in the application model. buffer The data to be used. This data must be in DBMS storage format. len The number of bytes to be copied from the buffer to the occurrence. Specify a negative value to indicate that more data is to follow. The absolute value of this number should not exceed the size of the buffer. Return Values Table 1. Values returned by ugputc Value Meaning >1 The total number of bytes copied by this call and by previous calls to ugputc (returned when Len > 1) 1 Uniface expects more data to be copied (returned when Len < 0) <0 The occurrence was not initialized with a call to ugput , or the entity is not a painted database entity Use Library: yrtl Description Use ugputc to move data from buffer to an occurrence of entity that was initialized with ugput . If entity is NULL or an empty string, the current entity is used. The data in buffer should be in DBMS storage format. Do not supply primary key values that are different from the values that were passed to ugput . Uniface does not check on this, and will use the values passed to ugputc . Use a negative value for len to indicate that there is more data to be moved to the occurrence. Use a non-negative value to indicate that the current block is the last block of data. This makes it possible to fill a large occurrence using a small buffer by repeated calls to ugputc . The processing is not complete until you call ugputc one last time with a non-negative value for len . Once this is done, further calls to ugputc will return -1 until ugput is called again to initialize a new occurrence. Example: Calling ugputc Repeatedly The following simple example illustrates how to fill an occurrence of the current entity with the value ‘ abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz ’ by repeated calls to ugputc with a length of -1. Note the concluding call to ugputc with a zero length; without that call, the data will not be shown in the component. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT void fill_occ () { int i; ugput(0, 0, 0); /* Initialize the occurrence */ for ( i=0; i<26; i++ ) { char ch = 'a'+i; gputc(0, &ch, -1); /* Add one alphabet character */ } ugputc(0, 0, 0); /* Terminate processing */ } Copy Related Links ugput Initialize an occurrence of the specified entity for subsequent calls to ugputc. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}